        <span class="comment-reply-link"><a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2009/05/19/salsa/?replytocom=259#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-259", "259", "respond", "373")'> &middot; Reply</a></span>		 		</div>
		<p>I see folks asking about the consistency of their salsa being a little off. I have found if you do blend it,only do it for like a half second.. just enough to break everything up smaller. Any further blending just ruins it. We like ours sorta chunky and natural-like..not blended.</p>
