		<p>I have never had a garden nor have I ever made salsa. However, this year I did a small garden that included jalepenos and serranos so I could make salsa. Can I use both in this recipe? Or should I make 2 different batches using the peppers individually.<br />
<strong>You can definitely use both! I change it up depending on what&#8217;s ripe in my garden at the time. Let me know how it turns out!</strong></p>
